USE WASD TO MOVE
PRESS SPACE TO JUMP
PRESS R TO RESTART

object.name: Text
object.text:
PRESS K TO PLACE EXPLOSIVE AT YOUR LOCATION
PRESS K AGAIN TO ACTIVATE EXPLOSIVE

object.name: Text
object.text:
THE CLOSER YOU ARE TO THE EXPLOSIVE
THE FARTHER IT PROPPELS YOU

object.name: Text
object.text: MOVING IN THE DIRECTION OF THE EXPLOSION MAKES YOU GO FARTHER
